name: Ostrich
description:
This is an archival giclée print created from an original oil and latex painting on canvas. The animal portrait is printed on Innova Soft White Cotton 280 gsm paper with archival Ink. Each print is made to order at a local print shop so please allow 2-3 business days for your order to be processed. Please note that the colors of the print may vary slightly from the colors of your screen. 

All images copyright Beth Mobilia, Thanks.
